        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4358",
        "content": "The chorister, even, was frequently among the missing, but was charitably supposed to be subject to the ague. Efforts were made to prevail upon the elderly part of the parish to permit the introduction of stoves with long funnels.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
